es from april  through march  before april  mr myers was the senior vice president and chief financial officer of cameron mr myers became senior vice president of cameron in  and served as general counsel and corporate secretary of cameron from  to  as well as president of its cooper energy services division from  until  prior to joining cameron he was senior vice president and general counsel of baker hughes incorporated an oilfield services and equipment provider and an attorney and partner with the law firm of fulbright  jaworski llp in houston texas franklin currently serves as independent director of ion geophysical corporation comfort systems holly frontier and forum energy technologies he is active in the local community and serves on the board of directors for the boy scouts of america sam houston council and is a trustee for the duchesne academy of the sacred heart an all girls’ school in houston franklin received a bachelor of science in industrial engineering from mississippi state university and a jd degree with honors from the university of mississippi robot check enter the characters you see below sorry we just need to make sure youre not a robot for best results please make sure your browser is accepting cookies type the characters you see in this image try different image continue shopping conditions of use privacy policy   amazoncom inc or its affiliates principles of corporate finance higher ed prek higher ed professional international search higher ed all categories prek  adult ed higher ed topics  ideas x menu sign in o  x view cart there are currently no items in your shopping cart contact change your selection if you wish to search for solutions in another division higher ed all categories prek  adult ed higher ed topics  ideas x sign in cart  contact mcgrawhill education higher education browse  shop browse  shop subjects business economics computer  information technology health professions vocational  career preparation education engineering